quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  2,6,"Inna allatheena kafaroo sawaonAAalayhim aanthartahum am lam tunthirhum layu/minoon"
  2,7,"Khatama Allahu AAala quloobihimwaAAala samAAihim waAAala absarihim ghishawatunwalahum AAathabun AAatheem"
  2,8,"Wamina annasi man yaqoolu amannabiAllahi wabilyawmi al-akhiri wamahum bimu/mineen"
  2,9,"YukhadiAAoona Allaha wallatheenaamanoo wama yakhdaAAoona illa anfusahum wamayashAAuroon"
  2,10,"Fee quloobihim maradun fazadahumuAllahu maradan walahum AAathabun aleemun bimakanoo yakthiboon"
  2,11,"Wa-itha qeela lahum latufsidoo fee al-ardi qaloo innama nahnumuslihoon"
  2,12,"Ala innahum humu almufsidoona walakinla yashAAuroon"
  2,13,"Wa-itha qeela lahum aminoo kamaamana annasu qaloo anu/minu kamaamana assufahao ala innahum humu assufahaowalakin la yaAAlamoon"
  2,14,"Wa-itha laqoo allatheena amanooqaloo amanna wa-itha khalaw ilashayateenihim qaloo inna maAAakum innamanahnu mustahzi-oon"
  2,15,"Allahu yastahzi-o bihim wayamudduhumfee tughyanihim yaAAmahoon"
  2,16,"Ola-ika allatheena ishtarawooaddalalata bilhuda famarabihat tijaratuhum wama kanoomuhtadeen"
